  speaker: 5
  lines:
  - isLeftSide: 1
    text: "Hayat k\u0131sa. Neden her an\u0131n tad\u0131n\u0131 \xE7\u0131karmayal\u0131m?"
  - isLeftSide: 0
    text: "Tad\u0131n\u0131 \xE7\u0131karmakla ka\xE7mak aras\u0131nda ince bir \xE7izgi
      var."
  - isLeftSide: 1
    text: "Hmm... Sen ilgin\xE7 birisin. Devam et."
  isNegative: 0
